SonarQube:- Continuos Code quality mgmt' tool
----------
Main purpose of implementing this tool is to perform Code review
This tool is a software quality managment tool--->sonar

- Static code analysis
- Code Review:--> validating the code against the standards wether the developers followed standards of developing the code
- Code coverage:-->no.of sourcecode lines tested by unittest cases

Maven/Apache Tomcat--->work only for java lang'
Sonarqube/Nexus/Jenkins--->Java as well as for other lang'

Sonarqube identifies issues such as:
------------------------------------
- Dulipcate code
- Coding standards
- Unit tests
- Complex code
- comments
- potential bugs
- Architeture/design

20+ lang' supported by SonarQube

SQL-->Structured Query Lang'--->MySQL(Database),PostgreSQL, Oracle, MS SQL--->Relational DB

Mongo DB

SonarQube--->H2 DB

Requirements:
-------------
2GB RAM
1--->OS
1--->SQ Server
t2.micro--->1CPU
t2.medium--->2CPU

SonarQube Architecture:
-----------------------

